Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> Who is down to recieve sha256 checksums, for our software, through HushList?

Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> I see value in it, personally

Content: [dscrd-hush] <Privatoshi> Sha256 is secure,simple, easy to decode

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-hush] <dukeleto> The value prop is "Having a secondary source to verify SHA sums that has it's own cryptographic proof that a SHA of binary X was declared at time Y by person Z"
